snippet.title: FIFA 15  - PS Vita Gameplay
snippet.description:
Remember when Messi played for Barcelona? :'(


Lucky for me he still did in 2015... Also lucky for me there is a beginner difficulty setting.


If you're going to play one FIFA game on the Vita I guess this is the most modern one. But they are all the same game with updated teams.
